**Steps to Reproduce**:

Both these methods produce IDE0045:
```
public void M2(object[]? parent, int i, object value)
{
    if (parent == null) // IDE0045
    {
        throw new KeyNotFoundException();
    }
    parent[i] = value;
}

public void N(object[]? parent, int i, object value)
{
    if (parent is { }) // IDE0045
    {
        parent[i] = value;
    }
